#

Spicy Garlic Shrimp Tacos

25 min
$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main CourseLunchDinner

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyMexican

Description

Flavorful shrimp tossed in a spicy garlic sauce, served in soft tacos with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • shrimp: 1 pound
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • cabbage (shredded): 2 cups
  • cilantro (chopped): 1/2 cup
  • avocado (sliced): 1
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
